Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:28.75,Default,dad,0,0,0,,Somali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.75,0:00:29.98,Default,dad,0,0,0,,Už si hore?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.28,0:00:34.16,Default,som,0,0,0,,Ešte je noc?
